column5: Was proud of my daughter. but her head is a little swollen now .. she is only 16  and handled herself well .  http://youtu.be/d51VRe8rV5c
Any word on numbers over as of what day?
Your daughter handled herself very well. Good for her for doing this her third year now.

Pretty Kewl!  I like the one old man in the background..... running and trying to hide from the camera! ha ha ha   Glad to see my step daughter did such a wonderful job presenting herself with the volunteer work she does. Now she just needs to learn to fish.
Now I know where her volunteering came from, now show her how to catch fish Ron.
